\dfrac {1+x}{1-x}=(1 + x + x^2 + x^3 + x^4 + ...)(1+x)=x^5+2x^4+2x^3+2x^2+2x+1 +...
 e^{2x}=1+2x+2x^2+\dfrac {4x^3}{3}+\dfrac { 2x^4}{3}+\dfrac {4x^5}{15}+... 
x<1
k\geq2
(2x/k-1)<0
 e^{2x}(1-x)=(1-x)\,\sum_{k=0}^\infty\frac{(2x)^k}{k!}=1+x+\sum_{k=2}^\infty\frac{2^{k-1}x^k}{(k-1)!}\,\left(\frac{2x}k-1\right)<1+x. 
\log 1+t < t
t>0
 2x>\frac{2x}{1-x}>\log\frac{2x}{1-x}=\log\frac{1+x}{1-x}. 
 e^{2x}>\frac{1+x}{1-x}. 
